column5: Anyone been this year and how is the fishing.
When the Sportsmans Journal was there a couple Sundays ago they didn't catch a walleye under 26".
The Sportsman Journal show was recorded two years ago....I'LL be there this weekend ..report on monday night.. KJmn.
That's right! The show with Wayne Jones was last summer, but they always show past episodes that are even older. I'll be interested to hear how the fishing was.
and the whole time I thought I was watching it live.
>The Sportsman Journal show was recorded two years >ago....I'LL be there this weekend ..report on monday night.. > KJmn.

will be going to dogtooth for first time this year and am interested on hearing a report, hopefully a good one.was also wondering if any of you have found a map for this lake. I have tried a ton of websites and have not had any luck. good luck to all and leave a few fish for us in july.
I was on Dogtooth and Kilvert this past weekend-send me an email at [email protected]
The lodge has the only map I am aware of. I have tried many map sources with no luck. The map is decent, but not great.
